    "UIName": "Megalodon",
    "Id": "chassisdef_megalodon_MLDN-F",
    "Name": "Megalodon",
    "Details": "The F configuration builds around a Clan Ultra AC/20 backed by a Targeting Computer, turning the entire arsenal into a precision weapon system. An ER Large Laser and ER Small Laser provide heat-efficient backup. Thirty rounds of Ultra AC/20 ammunition give it exceptional sustained firepower for an autocannon platform of this caliber. Nineteen double heat sinks keep the combined loadout manageable under sustained fire.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Combat Computer</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.17</color></b>",
    "Icon": "NEEDS_ICON"
